            "attack_type": "内生性偏倚",
            "patch_applied": "引入Group-based数据划分策略，强制执行样本独立性约束，阻断纵向/亲缘样本的跨集泄露。",
            "supporting_reference": "PMID: 27595325 (JAMIA; Saeb et al. highlights the impact of non-independent data on model generalizability)"
